      {
        "name": "Dual Shieldbearer",
        "type": "skill",
        "_id": "Da2IGLdbve78KoPI",
        "img": "systems/projectfu/styles/static/compendium/classes/guardian/guardian_dual_shieldbearer.png",
        "system": {
          "summary": {
            "value": ""
          },
          "description": "<p>You may now equip a <strong>shield</strong> in your <strong>main hand</strong> slot. As long as you have two shields equipped, you gain the benefits of both items and may treat them as the following combined two-handed melee <strong>brawling</strong> weapon:</p><table border=\"1\"><tbody><tr><td><p style=\"width:80px\"><strong>WEAPON</strong></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>ACCURACY</strong></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>DAMAGE</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"width:80px\">@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.2LyT2btVVPDPYY4h]{Twin Shields}</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>【MIG + MIG】</strong></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>【HR + 5】</strong> <strong>physical</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p>Brawling • Melee • Deals extra damage equal to your <strong>【SL】</strong> in <strong>defensive mastery</strong>.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><hr /><p>To <strong>automate</strong>, add the following @UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.2LyT2btVVPDPYY4h]{Twin Shields} to your character sheet. Navigate to the '<strong>Items</strong>\" tab where <strong>Twin Shields</strong> is located and press <strong>Ctrl+Click</strong> the icon in <strong>Equip?</strong> column. The item will be added to the <strong>Phantom Slot</strong>. Make sure this skill is added to your character sheet. Now you can equip shields on both your main and off hand slot.</p>",
